{"tid":685276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斥「地產霸權操控樓市」歪論　施永青：不努力耕作，以為鬥倒地主有飯吃","createTime":"2018-05-31T09:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T10:43:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c41a7c2bb1f0194cee3683d2d4188ee5483902be","tid":685276,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180531/s00001/161fdd04c24abb2cc079e00731556544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180531%2Fs00001%2F161fdd04c24abb2cc079e00731556544.jpg&h=5d9874f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「土地大辯論」仍在進行之際，中原地產主席施永青於《am730》專欄表示，今次辯論必須被駁倒的「歪論」，就是「香港房地產市場被地產霸權操控」。<br />\n<br />\n專欄題為〈本地民生需要 應獲優先照顧〉。施永青提到，有人認為增加土地供應沒用，因為「香港房地產市場已為地產霸權所操控」，但他認為，這是必須被駁倒的「歪論」，否則社會會把精力放在打倒地產霸權上，而非做好城市規劃。他形容，「這等同不去努力耕作，以為鬥倒地主就有飯吃一樣。結果全民投入政治鬥爭，全國進入大饑荒」。<br />\n<br />\n施永青稱，地產商無操控一切能力，「回想1997年至2003年期間，私人房屋供應量由每年二萬五千間，增至每年十萬間，加上亞洲的資金又被抽回美國，香港的樓價一瀉千里，合共跌了七成。地產商對此亦無能為力，大量炒家因而傾家蕩產，足見市場全為地產霸權操控的說法並不成立」，故「把精力放在打倒地產霸權上，只會把社會引上歪路」。<br />\n<br />\n施永青建議，政府增加土地供應同時，制定一些向本地用家首次置業傾斜的政策，「乾脆把房屋市場分割成兩個部分：一個是只供本地首次置業者參與的市場，另一個市場則全面開放，不再設辣招，無論是本地或是海外的投資者與用家都可以自由參與」。<br />\n<br />\n他又建議政府，先拿每年私人住宅用地中的一半，專門照顧本地首次置業者。賣地時亦可列明發展商建好樓宇後，只能賣給未有樓的本地用家等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180531/s00001/1527756500374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180531%2Fs00001%2F1527756500374&d=nmvs43czZi76FBiUJ2hPmVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=15b812e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180531%2Fs00001%2F1527756500374&h=dd7374c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180531/s00001/1527756500374</a>"},{"pid":"90742718d7c2801daf3ce1737354e7df1cd9dfce","tid":685276,"uid":13503,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:42:41.000Z","msg":"事實係晚清的確係打倒地主普通人先有飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6bd53eca37416a75727388af920a7b578ee11b","tid":685276,"uid":77196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:43:28.000Z","msg":"落去同毛澤東講啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9291cb3628b72d64d06dcb2368009d324810d4f","tid":685276,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:48:24.000Z","msg":"反共言論"},{"pid":"4c9dd4449526df8e444844d0c845b2d60c3d14b4","tid":685276,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:50:01.000Z","msg":"雖然外國啲大城市啲樓都係貴到癲<br />\n但係人哋只要搬遠少少就可以買返啲平樓 (around 1hr 車程)<br />\n香港? 唔通要搬返去深圳?"},{"pid":"8a7dd60f58cda9fc88b322347ef5729ad8fc8714","tid":685276,"uid":79919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc6bd53eca37416a75727388af920a7b578ee11b","tid":685276,"uid":77196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:43:28.000Z","msg":"落去同毛澤東講啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre